        "title": "How to check if a string is in this format &quot;12:30-14:30&quot; using regex",
        "body": "<p>I'm in a rush so I don't have time to review regex rules.<\/p>\n<p>I would like to know how do I check if a string is in this format &quot;12:30-14:30&quot;, where<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>the start time has to be before the end time.<\/li>\n<li>the minute section has to be &quot;:00&quot; or &quot;:30&quot;.<\/li>\n<li>the hour section is between &quot;08:&quot; and &quot;20:&quot;.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>Any help will be greatly appreciated! Thank you.<\/p>\n",
