        "is_accepted": true,
        "last_activity_date": 1689386611,
        "creation_date": 1689386611,
        "body": "<p>The regex answer is:<\/p>\n<pre><code>^((0[8-9]|1[0-9]|20):[03]0)-((0[8-9]|1[0-9]|20):[03]0)$\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>Note that this does not ensure that the start time is before the end time, you would need additional Java code to do that.<\/p>\n",
